{
  "claim_scope": "Exhaustive fixed-order diagnostic over the block-preserving shuffle family for the two-block block-6 fragile rows. Every order-specific full-extension search in this bounded family closes under vertex-circle quotient pruning. This is not an all-cyclic-order closure, not an all-extension bridge proof, not a proof of Erdos Problem #97, and not a counterexample.",
